<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: package_external_reference_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_external_reference_constraint">
The <b>package_external_reference_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of a representation when it is used as a package external reference.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_external_reference_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each representation with a name of 'package external reference'
shall contain a <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of 'design owner'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_external_reference_constraint.wr:WR2">
Each representation with a name of 'package external reference'
shall contain a <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of 'part number'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_external_reference_constraint.wr:WR3">
Each representation with a name of 'package external reference'
shall contain a <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of 'revision code'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_external_reference_constraint.wr:WR4">
Each representation with a name of 'package external reference'
shall contain a <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of 'product definition id'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: package_terminal_external_reference_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_terminal_external_reference_constraint">
The <b>package_terminal_external_reference_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of a
<express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> when it is used as a package terminal external reference.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_terminal_external_reference_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of 'package terminal external reference'
shall be a member of items for a representation with a name of 'package external reference'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: package_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint">
The <b>package_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains the
<express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> population members, that fill the role of ARM
<express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Package_terminal_external_reference"/>, so that the combination of ARM name
and ARM <express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Package_terminal_external_reference.associated_definition"/> attributes shall be unique within the population.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.package_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/> with a name of
'package terminal external reference' must have a unique combination of
description attributes and representation entities where the representations
have the <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/>s in their items attribute and the
representations have a name of 'package external reference'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: part_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.part_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint">
The <b>part_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains the
representation population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Part_terminal_external_reference"/>,
to have unique ARM <express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Part_terminal_external_reference.associated_definition"/> attributes with each ARM <express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Part_terminal_external_reference.feature_name"/>
attribute and ARM <express_ref linkend="Part_external_reference:arm:Part_external_reference_arm.Part_terminal_external_reference.feature_type"/> attribute combination.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Part_external_reference_mim.part_terminal_external_reference_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of representation with a description of 'part terminal external reference'
that has a common pair of description attributes on <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/>s in
its set of items with name attributes of 'feature type' and 'feature name' must have 
unique <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:mim:Physical_unit_usage_view_mim.physical_unit"/> entities that are referenced by a <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/>
definition.definition attribute and has one of said representations as the
<express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation"/>'s
 <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.property_definition_representation.used_representation"/> attribute.
</ext_description>

